test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc: If MODEA2 ne 0 and (INRELTO is 2 and INCNTFRQ is 6), then CHILDCOMM should be <= 2 or 8
full_desc: If Form A2, Q0d. MODEA2 is not equal to 0 (Form not completed), and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 2 (Child) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant)= 6 (less than once a month), then Q22. CHILDCOMM (Frequency of communication with children?) should be <= 2 or 8 (several times a year or less, or prefer not to answer)
test_logic: If (MODEA2 ne 0 and INRELTO=2 and INCNTFRQ =6) and (CHILDCOMM >2 and CHILDCOMM ne 8)

test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc: If MODEA2 ne 0 and (INRELTO=2 and INCNTFRQ < 6), then CHILDCOMM should be > 2 or 8
full_desc: If Form A2, Q0d. MODEA2 is not equal to 0 (Form not completed), and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 2 (Child) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant) is < 6 (more than monthly), then Q22. CHILDCOMM (Frequency of communication with children?) should be > 2 or 8 (several times a month or more, or prefer not to answer)
test_logic: If (MODEA2 ne 0 and INRELTO=2 and INCNTFRQ < 6) and (CHILDCOMM <= 2 or CHILDCOMM ne 8)

test_name: Consisitency in family/friend contact across forms
short_desc: If MODEA2 ne 0 and (INRELTO=5 and INCNTFRQ=6), then FRIENDCOMM should be <=2 or 8
full_desc: If Form A2, Q0d. MODEA2 is not equal to 0 (Form not completed),  and Form A2 Q1. INRELTO (relationship to participant) = 5 (Friend, neighbor, or someone known through family, friends, work, or community (e.g., church)) and Form A2 Q4a1. INCNTFRQ (primary contact freq w/participant) should not equal 6 (less than once a month), then Q23. FRIENDCOMM (Frequency of communication with friends?) should be <=2 or 8 (several times a year or less, or prefer not to answer)
test_logic: If (MODEA2 ne 0 and INRELTO=5 and INCNTFRQ =6) and (FRIENDCOMM >2 and FRIENDCOMM ne 8)

FRIENDCOMM (Frequency of communication with friends?) should be > 2 or 8 (several times a month or more, or prefer not to answer)
